[SN]TITLE[SN]
Arrest over alleged hate crime on Belfast bus

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A woman has been arrested after a report of a hate crime on a bus in Belfast.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
A woman allegedly assaulted a number of people on a bus travelling into the city after initially verbally abusing an elderly Polish couple shortly before noon on Tuesday.
Police also received a report of assault from the bus driver.
A 57-year-old woman is being questioned about disorderly behaviour, assault on police and three common assaults.
